The paper deals with lossy signal and image compression using partial differential equations (PDEs) for inpainting missing structures. This is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) research. The paper also discusses the optimization of data in the domain and codomain, which is related to information theory (cs.IT) and numerical analysis (cs.NA). Additionally, the paper presents algorithms for spatial and tonal optimization, which could fall under the category of signal processing (cs.SI).
